---
layout: base
permalink: /pillars/
title: "The Five Pillars"
description: "The Five Pillars of E5 Enclave — Environmental, Economic, Educational, Engagement, Emancipated. The structure of the harm is the structure of the remedy."
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "The Five Pillars" }
---
<header class="vc-page-head reveal">
  <div class="vc-page-eyebrow">— The Five Pillars —</div>
  <h1 class="vc-page-h">The structure of the harm is the structure of the <em>remedy.</em></h1>
  <p class="vc-page-deck">Five named domains of doctrine, each anchored to a flagship program or campaign. Together they form the architecture of repair.</p>
</header>

<section class="vc-pillars" style="background: var(--vc-bone); padding-top:24px;">
  <div class="vc-pillars-grid reveal">
    {% for pillar in pillars %}
    <a class="vc-pillar" href="/pillars/{{ pillar.slug }}/" aria-label="{{ pillar.name }} pillar">
      <div class="num">{{ pillar.numeral }}.</div>
      <div class="name">{{ pillar.name }}</div>
      <div class="body">{{ pillar.body }}</div>
      <div class="flag">{{ pillar.flagLabel }}<em>{{ pillar.flagName }}</em></div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="vc-feat" id="how-they-relate">
  <div class="vc-feat-rubric reveal">How the Pillars relate</div>
  <h2 class="vc-feat-h reveal">No pillar stands <em>alone.</em></h2>
  <div class="vc-feat-cols reveal">
    <div class="vc-feat-col">
      <h3><span class="roman">I.</span>Mutually reinforcing</h3>
      <p class="drop">Economic empowerment without education produces wealth without the capacity to govern it. Education without environmental stewardship produces knowledge disconnected from the systems that sustain life. <em>Each pillar reinforces the others.</em></p>
    </div>
    <div class="vc-feat-col">
      <h3><span class="roman">II.</span>Programs as proof</h3>
      <p class="drop">Each pillar names a flagship program or campaign that demonstrates the doctrine in practice — McCartney Academy under Educational, Lineage Farms · FarmBlock under Environmental, <em>Restitution 246</em> under Emancipated.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vc-feat-col">
      <h3><span class="roman">III.</span>The center holds</h3>
      <p class="drop">The Coalition convenes the work across pillars. Member organizations contribute capacity to one or more pillars without being absorbed into any of them. <em>Sovereign capacity, coordinated.</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
